trans-unit.source: Our regular monthly meeting. Find the agenda and minutes in our meeting folder.
Expert conducted a two day workshop on drug prevention.
Visited family after we heard that mother is seriously ill. She cannot get up. Children are taking care of housework. Told her to see doctor. We should follow up next week.
Discussed future of the child with the parents. They agree that changing school can be a good option. Will discuss further together with the child.
Called to ask for reason about absence. Mother made excuses but promised to send the child tomorrow.
Mother has called in the morning. Child cannot come to class because of fever.
Child was not in school whole last week again. When calling the mother she didn't know about it. Need to follow up urgently to discuss with the child and the guardians.
Visited the school and talked to the class teacher and principal. They are happy about the progress and behaviour.
Needs to work more for school
Discussed the child's progress with coaching teacher. He is still a weak student and needs more support. We should consider arranging an extra class for him. Discuss next social worker meeting.
Principal called us today. Our student got into a fight and was suspended for a week. Need to follow up with the child and discuss the matter.
Since the father has lost his job the family is struggling to survive. After home visits and discussion in our team we decided to refer them to a special support programme.

Child has failed this school year as she did not go to school regularly. After a long discussion with the child and her parents we agreed to support her to repeat the class and she promised to attend school regularly.
Teacher has let us know that he is very unfocused during class these days. Discussed with him - there are a lot of problems in the family currently.
She refused to listen to the teacher was disturbing the class. Did counselling session with her.
